text: Ali Saed Bin Ali El-Hoorie () is a terrorist working for Saudi Hizbollah. He was born in Saudi Arabia in 1965. In 1996 he bombed the Khobar Towers in Saudi Arabia. He is on the most wanted list of Terrorists from the FBI. == References == Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Islamist insurgents Category:Saudi Arabian people
